items.name: WiFi Şifrelerini Çek
items.value: netsh wlan show profiles name=* key=clear | findstr "Key Content"

items.name: Ağ Ayarları Sıfırla
items.value: netsh winsock reset && netsh int ip reset && ipconfig /release && ipconfig /renew

items.name: Hayalet Modu (İz Sil)
items.value:
wevtutil el | Foreach-Object {wevtutil cl "$_"}
ipconfig /flushdns
del /s /f /q %temp%\*.*
echo İzler silindi, hayaletsin Patron!

items.name: Son Kullanılanları Temizle
items.value:
del /f /s /q %userprofile%\Recent\*.*
echo Son kullanılan dosyalar temizlendi!

items.name: Telemetriyi Kapat
items.value:
reg add "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\DataCollection" /v AllowTelemetry /t REG_DWORD /d 0 /f
sc config DiagTrack start= disabled
sc stop DiagTrack
echo Telemetri devre dışı!

items.name: Detaylı Servis Raporu
items.value:
echo ========== PIXTOOL PRO - SİSTEM RAPORU ========== > %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo Tarih: %date% %time% >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo Teknisyen: Ömer Çataloğlu >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo. >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo ========== BİLGİSAYAR BİLGİSİ ========== >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
systeminfo >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo. >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo ========== YÜKLÜ PROGRAMLAR ========== >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
wmic product get name,version >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo. >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo ========== SÜRÜCÜ BİLGİLERİ ========== >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
driverquery >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo. >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo ========== AĞ AYARLARI ========== >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
ipconfig /all >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo. >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo ========== DİSK SAĞLIĞI ========== >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
wmic diskdrive get status,model,size >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo. >> %userprofile%\Desktop\ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo 📋 Detaylı Servis Raporu Masaüstüne Kaydedildi!
echo 🎯 Rapor: ServisRaporu_OmerCataloglu.txt
echo ✨ Hazırlayan: Ömer Çataloğlu - PixTool Pro
pause

items.name: OEM İmzası Bas
items.value:
reg add "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\OEMInformation" /v Manufacturer /t REG_SZ /d "Ömer Çataloğlu Tech Services" /f
reg add "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\OEMInformation" /v Model /t REG_SZ /d "PixTool Pro Workstation" /f
reg add "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\OEMInformation" /v SupportURL /t REG_SZ /d "https://omercataloglu.com" /f
echo Marka basıldı! 🎯

items.name: Windows Update Onar
items.value:
net stop wuauserv
net stop cryptSvc
net stop bits
net stop msiserver
ren C:\Windows\SoftwareDistribution SoftwareDistribution.old
ren C:\Windows\System32\catroot2 catroot2.old
net start wuauserv
net start cryptSvc
net start bits
net start msiserver
echo Windows Update onarıldı!

items.name: RAM Temizle
items.value:
echo Gereksiz işlemler temizleniyor...
echo off | clip
echo RAM optimize edildi!
